# Authors and Contributors

Huella Latam is a Digital Public Good developed by the United Nations
Development Programme (UNDP) under Project 01000983 — Climate Hub.

Copyright (c) 2024-2026 United Nations Development Programme (UNDP).
All deliverables produced under the project are the property of UNDP,
licensed to the public under the MIT License (see `LICENSE`).

This file lists the parties whose contributions are reflected in the
codebase. Contributions are recognised regardless of role.

## Project owner

- United Nations Development Programme (UNDP) — Climate Promise

## Maintainers

See `MAINTAINERS.md` for the active maintainer team and review
ownership.

## Contributors

A complete machine-generated contributor list can be obtained at any
time with:

    git shortlog -sne

External contributors are welcome via the process described in
`CONTRIBUTING.md`. Each contributor retains the copyright on their
contributions, which they license to the project under the same MIT
terms by submitting a pull request.
